sequenceDiagram
    participant Browser as Browser<br/>/reference/lore/:pack/:world
    participant React as React SPA<br/>(session-free route)
    participant API as FastAPI<br/>/reference/api/*
    participant Firewall as reference_visibility.py<br/>(firewall — unchanged)
    participant Content as sidequest-content<br/>(YAML packs + R2 assets)

    Browser->>React: Cold load (no session, no auth)
    React->>API: GET /reference/api/lore/:pack/:world
    API->>Firewall: classify() — strip keeper fields
    Firewall->>Content: Load world YAML + theme.yaml
    Content-->>Firewall: Raw world data
    Firewall-->>API: Public-only data (no keeper fields)
    API-->>React: JSON { sections[], theme_tokens{}, portrait_urls[] }
    Note over React: theme_tokens → CSS vars (session-free injector)
    Note over React: sections → POI / Cast / Map(d3-dag) / Timeline components
    React-->>Browser: Rendered reference page

    Note over API: /reference/* HTML routes DELETED
    Note over API: /reference/api/* JSON routes LIVE
    Note over Firewall: reference_visibility.py UNCHANGED